#: ../../tramp.texi:2821
msgid ""
"The remote file name syntax is similar to the syntax used by XEmacs.  A "
"remote file name has the form "
"@code{@trampfn{method,user@@host,path/to/file}}.  The @code{method} and "
"@code{user@@} parts are optional."
