"Type @kbd{s h @value{postfixhop}} for the minibuffer completion to "
"@samp{@value{prefix}ssh@value{postfixhop}}.  Typing @kbd{@key{TAB}} shows "
"host names @value{tramp} extracts from @file{~/.ssh/config} file, for "
